PreSonus Studio One Pro 2.6.2.25590 x86 x64 WIN

This release combines the cracks of teams AiR & UNiON









Studio One 2 is a new music creation and production application for Mac OSX and Windows XP / Seven that makes audio recording, MIDI sequencing, and audio mastering simple right out of the box, yet provides a wealth of professional features.




The Studio One 2.6.2 update includes the following features and fixes:

New features:

Support for Studio One Add-ons
The last ten autosaves are now automatically archived into the versions list
Optimized ARA data-saving to speed up autosave
